text: Md. Hase Uddin Dewan is a Jatiya Party (Ershad) politician and the former Member of Parliament of Gazipur-3. ==Career== Dewan was elected to parliament from Gazipur-3 as a Jatiya Party candidate in 1986. ==References== Category:Jatiya Party politicians Category:Living people Category:3rd Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
title: Md. Hase Uddin Dewan
